replies.body:
He has permanent bonus auto-attack damage that scales off AP and a ghost buff for his passive As an assassin, One of his abilities is a targeted skillshot nuke that giving him a shield scalling of his damage, alongside a passive that reduces enemy damage inflicted, while his no-cost W lets him recover mana for infinite sustain and deal instant damage to enemies. Moreover, he can deal AOE damage that slows for 90% and has a dash dealing damage every 2 seconds. 
He can use his all these abilities at the same time to burst anyone with immediate damage, making him the most mobile assassin capable of negative *tons of damage* with the resistances he's got and with the strong itemization he can get. 
{{champion:38}}
